Class GraphReasoner

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.semanticweb.owlapi.reasoner.impl.OWLReasonerBase
      • owltools.reasoner.GraphReasoner
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.geneontology.reasoner.OWLExtendedReasoner, org.semanticweb.owlapi.reasoner.OWLReasoner

    public class GraphReasoner
extends org.semanticweb.owlapi.reasoner.impl.OWLReasonerBase
implements org.geneontology.reasoner.OWLExtendedReasoner
    incomplete. the goal is to expose OWLGraphReasoner reachability queries via the reasoner interface. however, OWLReasoners do not support returning class expressions for superclass queries, so this provides an extra method
    Author:
    cjm
